{"tid":1509583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[經典重溫]林鄭月娥全家被北京挾持 沒有退路","createTime":"2019-08-27T01:43:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T06:58:13.000Z","uid":212509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f9dba027735d1f1af09bbd8af696e1ff7d8b00b","tid":1509583,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:43:09.000Z","msg":"見今朝大家咁熱烈討論政府新「風」<br />\n不如帶大家又回望一下過去<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">林鄭月娥全家被北京挾持 沒有退路</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭無理性地強硬態度，令外界頗為不解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有消息人士透露<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，林鄭之所以孤注一擲，是因為她被中央挾持，沒有選擇的餘地，「She has no choice」。<br />\n香港《壹週刊》引述不具名建制派消息人士的話說，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「<strong>若林鄭現時撤走條例，她及一家都玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>；若堅持多一陣，條例通過，縱使被（香港）人罵通街，但完成了（中共）中央派給的政治任務。林鄭相信香港人是善忘的。」<br />\n時事評論員唐靖遠分析，林鄭和她的前任一樣，唯中共的馬首是瞻，中共下令，林鄭不敢不聽。否則她的特首烏紗帽就要被摘了，而且她和家人也性命堪憂。<br />\n<br />\n【<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">政情】立會三日無會惹遐想 政圈看淡修例有轉機</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n反修例行動升級，不少人都期望有轉機，不過政圈目前仍然看淡撤回，因為政府研判周三的衝突，由示威者的充分準備、物資充裕、行動亦迅速，認為是有組織的「暴動」，針對的是政權，反修例只是手段並非目的。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>加上行政長官林鄭月娥一再表明不會撤回草案</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，班子口徑亦一致，即使是暫緩亦不可行，認為暫緩只是把痛苦延長，堅持反對者主要因誤解而非逃犯修例本質有問題，<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>沒有退讓的空間</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【政情】西環出手「團結」建制 續撐逃犯修例</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不少親中人士亦指逃犯爭議巳超越中港矛盾，涉及外國政府的介入，京官早已表示必須通過修例，這個立場在遊行後亦無改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，建制派亦早有心理準備，不論多少市民上街都要「企硬」，否則如何對得住撐修例的80萬網上聯署市民。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭而家死全家未？<br />\n中美貿易戰中國係咪因為暫緩所以已經輸到仆街？<br />\n今時今日仲信政府放出黎既「風」，究竟坐咗幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5136907a873cbf0c8d13a74686f89bea96834a","tid":1509583,"uid":35842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T01:43:27.000Z","msg":"小知識 - 原來機場控制唔只控制香港D機上落，<br />\n廣洲，深圳，澳門既飛機升降都會受香港指揮影響，搞到D飛升降唔到。。。。<br />\n大家千祈唔好搞到機場控制個班番唔到工啊 會好大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現有文宣集合 (Google Drive)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=e052e3ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=128hRA8sm5aa2jUlNJAzPtGkYt2_3n-z2</a><br />\n請隨便使用，用自己的方法幫忙發送文宣出去，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LoOsXdt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLoOsXdt.jpg&h=b1104862&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">每晚10點</span></strong></span>大家開大嗰窗嗌口號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當係抒發下或者互相鼓勵都好<br />\n<br />\n真係有人嗌㗎 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffit.tsoi%2Fvideos%2F189596038709864%2F&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrsbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=1f7a101f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fit.tsoi/videos/189596038709864/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1170684516349159/posts/23980